    <item>
      <title>阿达尼肯尼亚交易引发抗议、诉讼和听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/adani-s-kenya-dealings-spark-protests-lawsuits-and-hearings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 提出运营肯尼亚的主要机场，这一提议引发了抗议、参议院听证会和针对这个由亚洲第二大富豪控制的集团的诉讼，尽管该集团获得了在东非国家建设高压输电线的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/adani-s-kenya-dealings-spark-protests-lawsuits-and-hearings</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>战争经济成本上升，穆迪再次下调以色列评级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/israel-is-downgraded-by-moody-s-again-as-war-takes-economic-toll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于加沙近 12 个月的战斗以及与真主党的冲突加剧，以色列的经济成本不断增加，穆迪评级今年第二次下调了以色列的评级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/israel-is-downgraded-by-moody-s-again-as-war-takes-economic-toll</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 20:42:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Petrofac 债权人同意将大部分债务转换为股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/petrofac-creditors-agree-to-convert-majority-of-debt-into-equity</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Petrofac Ltd 已与一些主要利益相关者达成初步协议，债权人将把公司的大部分债务转换为股权，从而大幅稀释现有股东的股权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/petrofac-creditors-agree-to-convert-majority-of-debt-into-equity</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 19:11:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>农作物贸易商 Olam 因延迟提交棉花销售报告被罚款 330 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[农作物贸易商奥兰集团有限公司 (Olam Group Ltd.) 因延迟向美国农业部和商品期货交易委员会报告棉花销售情况，将支付 330 万美元罚款，此举可能会影响棉花价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/olam-to-pay-3-3-million-fine-for-delayed-cotton-sales-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 18:48:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>挑战加剧，大众汽车第二次下调业绩预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大众汽车集团今年第二次下调了业绩预期，警告称，在该公司与工会就可能的裁员和史无前例的工厂关闭问题展开斗争之际，需求减弱将削弱这家德国汽车制造商的盈利能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/volkswagen-lowers-forecast-again-on-waning-car-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 16:38:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平推出大规模刺激计划 旨在结束经济放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几个月来，尽管股市下跌、物价下跌、中国各地的不满情绪不断增长，但国家主席习近平似乎并未因经济增长放缓而感到不安。本周，他表明自己不愿再忍受任何痛苦。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/xi-s-big-stimulus-week-aims-to-draw-a-line-under-china-slowdown</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
